title: The Tao of Badass - Joshua Pellicer
description:
Tao of Badass - Joshua Pellicer

The Tao of Badass is a series of instructional videos that promises to give you, the average man, a crash course in becoming that man that all the women want.

You've all seen him, that confident man that?s slick as black ice and always surrounding by women with a telling flush on their cheeks at the bar.

What man in his right mind wouldn't want to be him, and to have his pick of the flock when women cross the party to check him out?

The Tao Of Badass Pros

The Tao of Badass is a series of videos, which keeps your interest and makes sure that you don?t lose interest the way you might with a book. Perfect for visual learners.

Engaging style. The Tao of Badass taps into the part of the male mind that wants to be cooler and more confident, and as such it keeps your interest.

Easy to take in. The Tao of Badass doesn?t take long to watch and it?s easy to break up into shorter segments so that you can take in information incrementally. And if there?s something you need to see two or three times, that?s simply not a problem for this medium.
The Tao of Badass comes with a money-back guarantee. Once you invest in this series you aren't necessarily committed for life.

Includes:

- Tao of Badass

- Bonus Books

- Breaking Up Like a Man

- Monogomy vs. Polyamory

- Never Get Cheated On

- The Friend Zone

- Authors Unabridged Audio Commentary

- 5 Week Body Language Mastery Course

- Confidence With Women: Subliminal Inner Confidence

- Hacking Attraction

- The Attraction Blueprint

- Advanced Coaches Prep Course (41 Sessions)
